      <div class="py-8 text-center text-2xl ">Nature and purpose of the business:</div>
  
      <div class="py-4 text-lg ">The Austrian Academy of Sciences (OEAW) has the legal duty to support the sciences and humanities in every respect. As a learned society, the OEAW fosters discourse and cooperation between science and society, politics and economy.</div>
